					<strong>Read detailed information via the official portal: </strong><a href="http://earthcube.org/group/cinergi">http://earthcube.org/group/cinergi</a>
					<!--By Chaowei (Phil) Yang | Edward M Armstrong | Thomas Huang | David Moroni | Yongyao Jiang | Yun Li-->
                </p>
                <!-- Date/Time 
